{"word":"ἀπόγονος","slug":"ἀπόγονος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπόγονος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀπογίγνομαι'><el>ἀπογίγνομαι</el></a>\n<p/><i>born</i> or <i>descended from</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>oriundus</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>descendants</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>ἀπόγονοι τεαί</el> thy <i>offspring</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}